<div2 type="poem" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                    <head>test on stop words</head>

                    <l n="tr">I call for the manager</l>
                    <l n="tr">The guy named Call should go there.</l>
                    <l n="tr">Call him please !</l>
                    <l n="tr">We're good, isn't it ?</l>
                    <l n="tr">"Oh, what perdition on our race!"</l>
                    <l n="tr">"How," says another, "can the case</l>
                    <l n="tr">Be quite so desp'rate as you've said?</l>
                    <l n="tr">For they're COLUMELLA contending who is head,</l>
                    <l n="tr">And lead a life from us disjoin'd,</l>
                    <l n="tr">Of sep'rate station, diverse kind."-</l>
                    <l n="tr">" But he, who worsted shall retire,</l>
                    <l n="tr">Will come into this lowland mire,</l>
                    <l n="tr">And with his hoof dash out our brains self</l>
                    <l n="tr">Defense wherefore self defense their rage to us pertains. columella"
</l>
                </div2>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
